<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">December 12, 2003 | Pages 14 and 15</font></P>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><P><B>OTHER STORIES BELOW:</B><BR>
